Version 2 of a Home Energy Centre using Raspberry Pi

This software displays:

Solar PV data
Solar Thermal (hot water) data
Curent Weather data


Work in progress.

aims are to:

rework the Resol collection code into Python [ done ] - no longer reliant on other code
